com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.refset.core.automap

Class SnomedRefSetAutoMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.refset.core.automap.SnomedRefSetAutoMapper

  • public class SnomedRefSetAutoMapper
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for mapping labels or IDs with SNOMED CT concepts. For performance optimization the automapper uses a recursive algorithm to get back a corresponding and appropriate equivalent.
